8. AI Routing System

RabbitOS can intelligently choose models.

Example logic:

Small Task → Local Model
Sensitive Task → Offline Model
Heavy Task → Cloud GPU
Code Task → Coding Agent
Vision Task → Vision Transformer

This reduces:

latency,

bandwidth,

cloud costs.


